This paper is about deep learning models and their convergence properties, which are typically studied in the field of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the application of these models to computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural networks (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper uses mathematical principles to derive its results, which could also place it in the category of data structures and algorithms (cs.DS).
